\c 147
\qc
\v 1 Hallelujah.
\q Praise the Eternal, for he is good;
\q2 make melody to our God, for he is gracious.
\q
\v 2 The Eternal restores Jerusalem,
\q2 he gathers the outcasts of Israel,
\q
\v 3 he heals the broken-hearted
