\q2 his orders and his laws to Israel;
\q
\v 20 never has he done so to other nations–
\q2 they know not his commands.

\c 148
\qc
\v 1 Hallelujah.
\q Praise the Eternal from the heavens,
\q praise him in the heights,
\q
\v 2 praise him, all his angels,
\q praise him, all his hosts,
\q
\v 3 praise him, sun and moon,
\q praise him, all stars of light,
\q
\v 4 praise him, heaven of heavens,
\q ye waters higher than the heavens!
\q
\v 5 Let them praise the name of the Eternal,
\q for he commanded and they were created,
\q
\v 6 he fixed them fast for evermore,
\q he set them boundaries that they should not pass.
\b
\q
\v 7 Praise the Eternal from the earth,
